Class Parser

  • java.lang.Object
    • filltheblankspython.Parser

  • public class Parser
extends java.lang.Object
    The Parser class is used to the get the data for the task from the given text file. It sets out which words are going to be blanked out and adds the necessary tags used for formatting when creating the JLabels later on.
